title: FF August 9, 2013
description:
[b]Annette De Burgh - Less Happier Lands[/b]

Publication Date: August 9, 2013

Set in the hostile climate of 1960s Britain, English teacher Diana Benton starts her new job at an exclusive Scottish school.

It is here she is confronted with the rebellious American pupil, Samantha Stevenson. 

A war of words soon spirals into a forbidden and passionate love that covers many years.

But as the years move on, troubled waters lie ahead.
